Class OutbindEvent

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.util.EventObject
      • org.smpp.ReceivedPDUEvent
        • org.smpp.OutbindEvent
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class OutbindEvent
extends ReceivedPDUEvent
    Created when outbind pdu is received from smsc. This event is created and passed to the OutbindEventListener by the OutbindReceiver.
    Version:

    Author:
